casebody.data:
Henry N. HARPER, petitioner,
v.
TUSCARAWAS COUNTY JOB & FAMILY SERVICES, et al. No. 15-9445. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 3, 2016.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States *81Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
